<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="114" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d114">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source"><persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1" type="from">Stalin</persName> to President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="to">Roosevelt</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d114fn1">Apparently sent via the Soviet Embassy, Washington.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-10">November 10, 1943</date>.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Personal and secret message from Premier <persName corresp="#p_SIV1">J.
                                V. Stalin</persName> to President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Franklin D. Roosevelt</persName></p>
                        <p>I have received Your message of November 8th.<note n="2" xml:id="d114fn2"><hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_71">p.
                                71</ref>.</note> I thank You for Your answer.</p>
                        <p>Your plan concerning the organization of our meeting in Iran, I accept. I
                            hope, and [<hi rend="italic">that</hi>] Mr. <persName corresp="#p_CC2">Churchill</persName> will agree with this proposal.</p>
                        <pb facs="0171" n="79" xml:id="pg_79"/>
                        <p>By November 22nd, Mr. <persName corresp="#p_MVM1">V. M.
                                Molotov</persName> and our military representative will arrive in
                            Cairo, where together with you they will agree upon everything necessary
                            in connection with our meeting in Iran.</p>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">November</hi> 10, 1943.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>